    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/a8000ef47f3ca16c8aa38dc69251a21e.avif?t=1749704798\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>欢迎来到梦幻般的交错节拍的世界！<br>原以为谁都无法通关的节奏游戏被音游超人们彻底清除了，所以大大提高了音量和质量之后回归了！你能驾驭得了这个节奏吗！<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/8d0d47ec93d65002fde274d5c04fc35f.poster.avif?t=1749704798\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/8d0d47ec93d65002fde274d5c04fc35f.webm?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/8d0d47ec93d65002fde274d5c04fc35f.mp4?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>是只需要在到达图形顶点上的〇时的一瞬间按下对应的键的简单的游戏！好吧...图形会逐渐增加...<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/ecfeda108cdfbc8bf38cc8330baa0d0a.poster.avif?t=1749704798\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/ecfeda108cdfbc8bf38cc8330baa0d0a.webm?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/ecfeda108cdfbc8bf38cc8330baa0d0a.mp4?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在舞台选择中也安装了休止符模式和反拍模式等更复杂的模式。<br>和朋友在排行榜上竞争节奏感吧！<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/7c921ee310209d5742594b5864a7f8ce.poster.avif?t=1749704798\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstat